        "liquid": "{% comment %}Comparison Table DE{% endcomment %}\n<div class=\"sv-compare-section\">\n  <h2 class=\"sv-compare-title\">Warum SkinVeil™ alles andere übertrifft.</h2>\n  <div class=\"sv-compare-table\">\n<div class=\"sv-compare-header\">\n  <div class=\"sv-col-feature\"></div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-us\">\n    <div class=\"sv-us-badge\">\n      <span class=\"sv-us-logo\">SORELYA</span>\n      <span class=\"sv-us-sub\">SkinVeil™</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-other\">Foundation</div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-other\">Selbst-bräuner</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"sv-compare-row\">\n  <div class=\"sv-col-feature\">Deckt Besenreiser, Dehnungsstreifen und Narben</div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-us\"><span class=\"sv-check\">&#10003;</span></div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-other\"><span class=\"sv-partial\">~</span></div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-other\"><span class=\"sv-cross\">&#10005;</span></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"sv-compare-row\">\n  <div class=\"sv-col-feature\">Kein Abfärben auf Kleidung, Bettwäsche oder Handtüchern</div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-us\"><span class=\"sv-check\">&#10003;</span></div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-other\"><span class=\"sv-cross\">&#10005;</span></div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-other\"><span class=\"sv-cross\">&#10005;</span></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"sv-compare-row\">\n  <div class=\"sv-col-feature\">Wasserfest, schweißresistent und sonnensicher</div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-us\"><span class=\"sv-check\">&#10003;</span></div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-other\"><span class=\"sv-cross\">&#10005;</span></div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-other\"><span class=\"sv-partial\">~</span></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"sv-compare-row\">\n  <div class=\"sv-col-feature\">Trocknet in 10 Minuten</div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-us\"><span class=\"sv-check\">&#10003;</span></div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-other\"><span class=\"sv-partial\">~</span></div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-other\"><span class=\"sv-cross\">&#10005;</span></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"sv-compare-row\">\n  <div class=\"sv-col-feature\">Jederzeit unter der Dusche entfernbar</div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-us\"><span class=\"sv-check\">&#10003;</span></div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-other\"><span class=\"sv-check sv-check-dark\">&#10003;</span></div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-other\"><span class=\"sv-cross\">&#10005;</span></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"sv-compare-row\">\n  <div class=\"sv-col-feature\">Präziser Farbton-Match, kein Orangestich</div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-us\"><span class=\"sv-check\">&#10003;</span></div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-other\"><span class=\"sv-partial\">~</span></div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-other\"><span class=\"sv-cross\">&#10005;</span></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"sv-compare-row sv-last-row\">\n  <div class=\"sv-col-feature\">Kein DHA, keine chemischen Bräunungsmittel</div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-us\"><span class=\"sv-check\">&#10003;</span></div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-other\"><span class=\"sv-check sv-check-dark\">&#10003;</span></div>\n  <div class=\"sv-col-other\"><span class=\"sv-cross\">&#10005;</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<style>\n.sv-compare-section{padding:36px 16px 28px;background:#ffffff;font-family:-apple-system,'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif}\n.sv-compare-title{font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:24px;font-style:italic;color:#1a1a2e;margin:0 0 24px;line-height:1.3;text-align:left}\n.sv-compare-table{width:100%;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden}\n.sv-compare-header,.sv-compare-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 56px 56px 56px;align-items:center;gap:0}\n.sv-compare-header{margin-bottom:4px}\n.sv-compare-header .sv-col-feature{background:transparent}\n.sv-col-us{background:linear-gradient(180deg,#2a2040 0%,#8b7355 100%);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:16px 8px;border-radius:14px 14px 0 0}\n.sv-us-badge{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px}\n.sv-us-logo{font-size:10px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase}\n.sv-us-sub{font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:11px;font-style:italic;color:#c9a84c}\n.sv-col-other{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#999;text-align:center;padding:12px 4px;line-height:1.3;background:#efefef;border-radius:14px 14px 0 0;margin:0 2px}\n.sv-compare-row{border-bottom:1px solid #ece8e4}\n.sv-compare-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}\n.sv-col-feature{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;line-height:1.4;background:#f5f5f5;padding:14px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid #ece8e4}\n.sv-compare-row .sv-col-us{background:linear-gradient(180deg,#2a2040 0%,#8b7355 100%);border-radius:0;padding:14px 8px}\n.sv-last-row .sv-col-us{border-radius:0 0 14px 14px}\n.sv-compare-row .sv-col-other{background:#efefef;border-radius:0;padding:14px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;font-weight:400;margin:0 2px}\n.sv-last-row .sv-col-other{border-radius:0 0 14px 14px;border-bottom:none}\n.sv-check{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.6);color:#fff;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto}\n.sv-check-dark{border-color:rgba(0,0,0,0.2);color:#555;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.06)}\n.sv-cross{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;background:#1a1a2e;color:#fff;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto}\n.sv-partial{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;background:#b8a080;color:#fff;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto;line-height:1}\n</style>",
